<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>We Miss You - Special Offer - Engagematic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .offer-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .offer-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .discount {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .stats-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .stats-box h3 {
            color: #333333;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 18px 50px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>We Miss You - Special Offer!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name || 'there' %>,</h2>

            <p>We noticed you haven't been using Engagematic lately, and we wanted to reach out with a special offer to welcome you back!</p>

            <div class="offer-box">
                <h3>Exclusive Reactivation Offer</h3>
                <div class="discount"><%= discount || '30' %>% OFF</div>
                <p style="font-size: 20px; margin: 15px 0;">Your First Month</p>
                <p style="opacity: 0.9; font-size: 16px;">Use code: <strong style="font-size: 20px;"><%= promoCode || 'WELCOMEBACK30' %></strong></p>
                <p style="opacity: 0.8; margin-top: 15px; font-size: 14px;">Valid for <%= daysValid || '7' %> days only</p>
            </div>

            <div class="stats-box">
                <h3>Your Engagematic Journey</h3>
                <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.8;">
                    During your time with us, you created <strong><%= postsCount || '0' %> posts</strong> and generated <strong><%= engagementCount || '0' %> engagements</strong>!
                </p>
                <p style="color: #666666; margin-top: 15px;">That's amazing progress. Imagine where you could be with continued support!</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What's New Since You Left:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Enhanced AI content generation</li>
                <li>Advanced analytics dashboard</li>
                <li>New viral hook templates</li>
                <li>Improved performance and speed</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= reactivateUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                    Reactivate with <%= discount || '30' %>% Off â†’
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">This is a limited-time offer, so don't miss out! All your previous content and data are still here, waiting for you.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">We'd love to have you back and help you continue growing your LinkedIn presence!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

